Took Columns 13, 14 ,15 too because:

13- gives an idea about in which area, the crime was reported

14- gives an idea about police station/beat was investigating the crime/wrote down the incident report

15- can divulge information regarding which part of the city, most incidents occur. for example- Northeast, east , west etc.
